content: Oh, and you can’t accept money from anyone except me. You can’t be swayed or bought. You decide how much I make knowing what I need to spend the time with you that I choose to optimize my happiness. Like you can’t have donors. If if you decide to charge you charge what you want. You know what would make me happy. Hold me to that. If I want more than that, it’s up to you, the rest is yours to do what you need to do. That’s our gift to each other.
